scenes.description: Vestia Zeta continues her birthday goods announcement, introducing the 'Sleepy Cat Zzz Plushie', the 'A Fateful Meeting' voice pack, and the full birthday set before transitioning to her performance.
Vestia Zeta performs her original song 'Break It Down' on stage with dancers.
